<td height="299"><ul>
  <li class="style20"><font class='cfont10'>Your email address will be maintained in the CGVA Data Base if you have ever registered for a CGVA League OR Tournament OR you have ever requested to be added to the CGVA Data Base OR you have registered with MyCGVA. </font></li>
