  <li class="style20"><font class='cfont10'>You may change information maintained in the CGVA Data Base by updating  your MyCGVA profile OR by sending the new information to <a href="mailto:cgva@cgva.org ">cgva@cgva.org</a></font>. </li>
  <li class="style20"><font class='cfont10'>Your email address will only be used to send information about:
</font>
<ul>
