<li><font class='cfont10'>Other information deemed appropriate by the CGVA Board of Directors </li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="style20"><font class='cfont10'>Your contact information will not be shared with other organizations. </font></li>
<li class="style20"><font class='cfont10'>Typically, all correspondence with you will be via Email. Very rarely, CGVA will send out physical mailings to the physical address you provide to CGVA. </font></li>
